sentences: Jeff Chang Shin-che (Chinese: 張信哲; born 26 March 1967) is a Taiwanese singer and actor, who is known for his numerous chart-topping sentimental Mandarin pop ballads.
Since 1989 he has released a string of highly successful albums and is known as the "Prince of Love Ballads" in the Chinese pop world.
He became Taipei's leader in a stage theatre team in 2011.
In 2016, Chang participated in the fourth season of the Chinese reality show I Am A Singer and eventually achieved second place.
